TITLE: Episode 36 - Waco pt. 2 of 3 Operation Showtime (MLGA recast)
DESCRIPTION: Yesterday was the 27th anniversary of the slaughter of the Branch Davidians in Waco, Texas. Today, I am sharing the second of a three part miniseries about those events. It is a recast from the Make Liberty Great Again podcast. Strap in, because this is going to hurt.
